    <p class="text-white/80 mb-6 max-w-xl mx-auto">Industrial oil centrifuge systems that pay for themselves in under 12 months. Kidney-loop configurations for turbine lube, hydraulic, and compressor oil. Factory tested from Warren, MI.</p>
